{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/sian-taylor-phillips","content_id":"285c87cc-5af1-4d08-bd50-ea0d6118f6b0","description":"Sian Taylor-Phillips is Professor of Population Health at the University of Warwick, specialising in evaluation of medical tests and screening programmes. She leads Warwick Screening, a team of researchers which synthesises evidence for national policy-makers, and undertakes primary research across several screening programmes. Sian has a particular interest in evaluating the benefits and harms of different versions of breast cancer screening and holds several grants in this area.","details":{"body":"<p>Sian Taylor-Phillips is Professor of Population Health at the University of Warwick, specialising in evaluation of medical tests and screening programmes. She leads Warwick Screening, a team of researchers which synthesises evidence for national policy-makers, and undertakes primary research across several screening programmes. Sian has a particular interest in evaluating the benefits and harms of different versions of breast cancer screening and holds several grants in this area.</p>\n","full_name":"Professor Sian Taylor-Phillips","image":{"alt_text":"Professor Sian Taylor-Phillips","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/62b2ed8dd3bf7f0af7e9b019/s465_Sian_Taylor_Phillips.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2022-06-14T09:29:25+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/sian-taylor-phillips","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/sian-taylor-phillips","base_path":"/government/people/sian-taylor-phillips","content_id":"285c87cc-5af1-4d08-bd50-ea0d6118f6b0","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-06-22T10:23:09Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Professor Sian Taylor-Phillips","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sian-taylor-phillips","withdrawn":false}],"ro